items.reviewContent:
Very poor and pathetic customer service. Order was placed on 12th November and despite multiple follow-ups, correct information was never given on delivery status. Order was delivered today on 25th November after I gave them the ultimatum that I will not accept delivery if order was not delivered today.

Suffice to say, order was received in a poor state of condition. The packaging was torn from multiple places and the top of the dispenser has multiple scratch marks on its body indicating that the dispenser was previously being used someplace and that they had hurriedly packed it up and sent to me after it became apparent the order was going to be cancelled.

As to it's market price, flagship store is charging more than what it's currently available at in the market.

My experience with Dawlance has not been reliable at all. Won't be ordering again from them.

P.S: I would've refunded this immediately given it's condition, but given how long it took them to deliver, not gonna bother.
